By Golem Fan on Friday, April 12, 2002 - 11:50 am:

By WHT Junior on Friday, April 12, 2002 - 12:50 pm:

Golem Fan, you'll want to skip that error, and burn the CD anyway. CloneCD is just warning you that the Image and CCD don't match. They won't match, since the track info in the Image file will now be different from the actual tracks on the CD. MR reads the Subcode, and ignores the actual tracks.
